schema_id: dominium.render.renderable
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: stable
description: Deterministic renderable record resolved from a perceived semantic item.
fields:
  - renderable_id
  - semantic_id
  - primitive_id
  - transform
  - material_id
  - layer_tags
  - label
  - lod_hint
  - flags
  - extensions
